link="/donations/" title="donate"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/trx_sc_content][/vc_column][/vc_row]";s:10:"post_title";s:32:"LightHouse Header Short /2 rows/";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:19:"header-short-2-rows";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-10-25 06:45:24";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-10-25 06:45:24";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:63:"http://lighthouse.ancorathemes.com/layouts/header-short-2-rows/";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:11:"cpt_layouts";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:2;a:23:{s:2:"ID";s:2:"32";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-06-22 11:56:44";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-06-22 11:56:44";s:12:"post_content";s:5097:"[vc_row][vc_column][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h4" title_align="center" title="Our Support Policy"][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1495456306665{padding-right: 20px !important;}"]
<ul>
 	<li>To get a pre-purchase advice, you may post in the theme’s forum.</li>
 	<li>To get a response more promptly, you are recommended to use our Ticket-system.</li>
 	<li>We try to answer your questions within 1-10 hours. However, if any delay occurs, it doesn’t mean that we forgot about you. Some of the issues require testing and analyzing, so we can resolve it effectively.</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<ul>
 	<li>Please note! We do not provide support, if you do not have the purchase code.</li>
 	<li>Item support does not include:
<ol>
 	<li>Customization and installation.</li>
 	<li>Support for third party software and plugins.</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space alter_height="small" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h4" title_align="center" title="How to use our Support System" description="ThemeREX technical support is always there to assist their users with all the technical questions regarding their products."][vc_empty_space height="32px " alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="33" img_size="525x300"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_column_text]
<ol>
 	<li>In the ‘Item Details’ there is a clickable banner “Support Sys”, which leads you to tickets.</li>
 	<li>Or you may simply follow this link: <a href="https://ancorathemes.ticksy.com/">ancora.ticksy.com.</a></li>
 	<li>Enter your purchase key and register in the system.</li>
 	<li>To avoid a confusion, please use your own ThemeForest login in Support System.</li>
 	<li>Fill out the ticket form.</li>
</ol>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_empty_space alter_height="small" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h4" title_align="center" title="How to find a purchase key"][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="34" img_size="650x400"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="7em" alter_height="none" hide_on_mobile="1"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1495459925135{padding-right: 40px !important;}"]
<ul>
 	<li>Open the “downloads” tab in your account.</li>
 	<li>Find our theme in the list of products.</li>
 	<li>Click “download” button, and in the drop-down menu select “license certificate &amp; purchase code”.</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h4" title_align="center" title="Hosting" description="Recommended hostings:"][vc_empty_space alter_height="small" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_column_text]
<p style="text-align: center;">Ancora team offers only the best products and services and recommends them to their customers. One of the most important services is HOSTING. Unlike any cheap hostings that usually have limited resources which causes many problems to the site owners, quality hosting gives a client a fair amount of resources sufficient for any website and any task. By using quality hosting you can rest assured that your site will work smoothly. If you happen to use such hosting with limited resources (e.g. GoDaddy!), you may experience issues with “one-click install” feature. In that case, you are always welcome to contact our support team to get qualified help.</p>
[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row"][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="39" img_size="" alignment="center" onclick="custom_link" link="http://www.inmotionhosting.com"][vc_column_text]
<p style="text-align: center; margin: 0;"><a href="https://secure1.inmotionhosting.com/cgi-bin/gby/clickthru.cgi?id=themerex">http://www.inmotionhosting.com</a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Get more than <strong>30% discount</strong> on a hosting plan.</p>

<h4 style="text-align: center;">Accordion &amp; Tabs</h4>
<div class="dummy"></div>
[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_tta_accordion shape="round" c_icon="chevron" c_position="right" active_section="1"][vc_tta_section title="Sed ut perspiciatis?" tab_id="1498134750982-8ec1bd0b-0ef3"][vc_column_text]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat. Ut wisi enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci tation ullamcorper suscipit.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Duis autem eum iriure?" tab_id="1498134751122-22538824-bd18"][vc_column_text]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat. Ut wisi enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci tation ullamcorper suscipit.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Consectuer adipng?" tab_id="1498134801669-1d72e493-1e71"][vc_column_text]Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetuer adipiscing elit, sed diam nonummy nibh euismod tincidunt ut laoreet dolore magna aliquam erat volutpat. Ut wisi enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exerci tation ullamcorper suscipit.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md vc_hidden-sm"][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_tta_tabs shape="round" spacing="" alignment="center" active_section="1" no_fill_content_area="true"][vc_tta_section title="Mission" tab_id="1498134875103-21c2edd0-c6e4"][vc_column_text]
<h6 style="text-align: center;">We are a non-profit organization. Our goal is to provide every individual with special needs the support, friendship and inclusion that they deserve.</h6>
&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: center;">With this inspiration, the lives of the families we serve are enhanced while the volunteers reap the rewards of selfless giving. We create friendship in the lives of individuals with special needs and provides an opportunity to become a contributing member of the community.</p>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="Goals" tab_id="1498134875241-cad720dd-2c05"][vc_column_text]

Voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium, totam rem aperiam, eaque ipsa quae ab illo inventore veritatis et quasi architecto beatae vitae dicta sunt explicabo. Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt. Neque porro quisquam est, qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, consectetur, adipisci velit, sed quia non numquam eius modi tempora incidunt ut labore et dolore magnam aliquam quaerat voluptatem. Aliquam bibendum lacus quis nulla dignissim faucibus. Sed mauris enim, bibendum at purus aliquet, maximus molestie tortor. Sed faucibus et tellus eu sollicitudin. !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1502965493373{padding-right: 3rem !important;padding-left: 3rem !important;}"]
<p style="text-align: center;">Types of special needs vary in severity. People with autism, Down syndrome, dyslexia, blindness, ADHD, or cystic fibrosis, for example, may be considered to have special needs. However, special needs can also include cleft lips, or missing limbs.</p>
[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile="" css=".vc_custom_1502965581566{margin-top: -0.25rem !important;}"][trx_sc_button type="default" color_style="dark" align="center" icon_position="left" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile="" link="/scholarships/" title="more about us"][vc_empty_space alter_height="huge" hide_on_mobile="" css=".vc_custom_1502965613430{margin-top: 2.55rem !important;}"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" icons_position="left" css=".vc_custom_1502965151048{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}" offset="vc_col-sm-offset-1"][vc_empty_space alter_height="huge" hide_on_mobile="" css=".vc_custom_1502965852833{margin-top: 1.4rem !important;}"][vc_single_image image="361" img_size="full" alignment="center" css=".vc_custom_1502969764359{margin-bottom: -1rem !important;}"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6" icons_position="left"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3" icons_position="left"][trx_sc_content type="shadowed" size="none" paddings="medium" align="center" number_position="br" title_style="default" css=".vc_custom_1502970476690{background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1502970167552{background-color: #ffffff !important;}"]
<h4>$345,599</h4>
<span class="trx_addons_events_small">DONATED FOR KIDS WITH SPECIAL</span><span class="trx_addons_events_small">NEEDS IN 2016</span>[/vc_column_text][/trx_sc_content][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile="" css=".vc_custom_1502970815402{margin-top: -1.8rem !important;}"][trx_sc_testimonials type="simple" orderby="none" title_style="default" ids="630"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/6" icons_position="left"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space alter_height="huge" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row]";s:10:"post_title";s:14:"Home Say Hello";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:11:"say-hello-2";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-08-23 14:33:23";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-08-23 14:33:23";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:68:"http://lighthouse.ancorathemes.com/?post_type=cpt_layouts&#038;p=635";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:11:"cpt_layouts";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:247;a:23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"651";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-08-17 13:42:38";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-08-17 13:42:38";s:12:"post_content";s:3352:"[vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content_no_spaces" equal_height="yes"][vc_column width="1/3" icons_position="left" offset="vc_col-sm-offset-1"][vc_empty_space alter_height="huge" hide_on_mobile="" css=".vc_custom_1502974138897{margin-top: 1rem !important;}"][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h4" title_align="center" title="Mission"][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile="" css=".vc_custom_1502974369842{margin-top: -0.1rem !important;}"][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h4" title_align="center" subtitle="We are a non-profit organization. Our goal is to provide every individual with special needs the support, friendship and inclusion that they deserve." css=".vc_custom_1502974640170{padding-right: 2rem !important;padding-left: 2rem !important;}"][vc_tta_tabs shape="round" spacing="" tab_position="bottom" alignment="center" active_section="1" no_fill_content_area="true"][vc_tta_section title="mission" tab_id="1498475487619-7bed29a2-3ad3"][vc_column_text]
<p style="text-align: center;">The term Special Needs is a short form of Special Education Needs and is a way to refer to students with disabilities. The term Special Needs in the education setting comes into play whenever a child's education program is officially altered from what would normally be provided.</p>

[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="goals" tab_id="1498475487664-906741ba-4d09"][vc_column_text]
<p style="text-align: center;">More narrowly, it is a legal term applying in foster care in the United States, derived from the language in the Adoption and Safe Families Act. It is a diagnosis used to classify children as needing "more" services than those children without special needs who are in foster care.</p>

[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title="beliefs" tab_id="1498475519147-80e89ff1-97ad"][vc_column_text]
<p style="text-align: center;">In the United States, special needs is a term used in clinical diagnostic and functional development to describe individuals who require assistance for disabilities that may be medical, or psychological. For instance, the Diagnostic Statistical Manual of Mental Disorders.</p>
